  "instructions": [
    "Pound garlic and ginger in a mortar and pestle until smooth.",
    "Heat coconut oil in a pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the tilapia fillets and cook for 2-3 minutes on each side, until crispy and cooked through.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together creme fraiche, fish sauce, lime juice, palm sugar and a pinch of salt and pepper.",
    "To assemble the dish, place a tilapia fillet in each donabe, then spoon the garlicky sauce over the top and garnish with cilantro."
